{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2016}} {{Infobox museum | name = Mantua Municipal Museum | native_name = Museo Municipal de Mantua | native_name_lang = Spanish | image = | imagesize = | caption = | coordinates = | established = {{Start date|1980|12|23|df=y}} | location = [[Mantua, Cuba|Mantua]], [[Cuba]] | director = Rodolfo Álvarez Gavilán | website = <!-- {{URL|example.com}} --> }} '''Mantua Municipal Museum''' is a [[museum]] located in the José Martí street [[Mantua, Cuba|Mantua]], [[Cuba]]. The building was constructed in 1901. It was established as a museum on 23 December 1980.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.cnpc.cult.cu/institucion/259 | title=Museo Municipal de Mantua | publisher=Patrimonio cultural / Consejo Nacional Cuba | accessdate=1 January 2016 }}</ref>
